name: face poser
description:
New version. Basically the same data set, but new training options. I'm not sure it's better.

Implied fellatio is now a tag it seems to recognize, for more circular shape to the open mouth.

Share your results! The frames for the new gif are in the training data download.

this model is meant to help pose faces for lewd scenes

  • open mouth: combine with tongue and uvula for wide open

  • closed mouth: combine with cum in mouth, for dribbling cum

  • teeth: combined with lower and upper to determine mouth pose

  • tongue: overtrained on tongue out, so put tongue out in the negative prompt if you want the tongue in the mouth

  • lower teeth: affects the angle you see the mouth

  • upper teeth: affects the angle you see the mouth

  • closed eyes: eyes weren't a focus, but as you can see in the sample, it helps a lot

  • open eyes

  • rolling eyes

  • one eye closed: wink

  • half-closed eye

  • cum in mouth: combine with cum on tongue in the negative for cum in the back of the mouth

  • oral invitation: makes the pose more direct, can be combined with hand gesture, but the results are small

  • cum on tongue

  • close-up: helps increase detail for inside the mouth, increase strength for inside the mouth,

  • blush? I'm not actually sure what impact this has on blush, it works well, transitions well, but that might just be the AOM3 model

Let me know what you think about the gif in the preview; do you think they're worth it for showing off models?

Honestly, it took me almost as long to make that, as it took to train the model.
